text: Llano Grande is a corregimiento in La Pintada District, Coclé Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 6,901 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 4,816; its population as of 2000 was 6,026. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Coclé Province
